snippet.title: Chipped Trailer | A Dual Control Stalker-Puzzle Horror Game
snippet.description:
Play the prologue of the game: https://t3rrifk.itch.io/chipped

Trapped in an underground facility, use your brain implant to control a robot to help you escape—but it's also trying to kill you.
